<section class="vat section" id="what-is-vat">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vat__grid">
      <div class="vat__content">
        <p class="section-label">Education</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What is Vibration Acoustic Therapy?</h2>

        <p class="vat__text">
          Vibration Acoustic Therapy (VAT) is a non-invasive therapeutic approach that uses
          low-frequency sound waves — typically between 30 and 120 Hz — to create gentle vibrations
          that penetrate deep into the body. These vibrations are delivered through specially designed
          equipment that translates sound into physical sensation.
        </p>

        <div class="vat__how">
          <h3 class="vat__how-title">How It Works</h3>
          <div class="vat__steps">
            <div class="vat__step">
              <span class="vat__step-num">01</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Sound Becomes Vibration</h4>
                <p>Specific therapeutic frequencies are selected based on your needs and converted into physical vibrations through transducers in the treatment surface.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vat__step">
              <span class="vat__step-num">02</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Deep Tissue Penetration</h4>
                <p>Unlike surface-level treatments, these vibrations travel through muscle, fascia, and bone — reaching areas that hands and traditional methods cannot.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vat__step">
              <span class="vat__step-num">03</span>
              <div>
                <h4>Cellular Response</h4>
                <p>Your body responds at the cellular level: increased blood flow, reduced inflammation, muscle relaxation, and activation of the parasympathetic nervous system.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="vat__benefits">
          <h3>Research-Backed Benefits</h3>
          <ul class="vat__benefit-list" role="list">
            <li>Significant reduction in chronic pain and muscle tension</li>
            <li>Decreased anxiety and cortisol levels</li>
            <li>Improved sleep quality and duration</li>
            <li>Enhanced circulation and lymphatic drainage</li>
            <li>Accelerated muscle recovery after exercise</li>
            <li>Reduced symptoms of fibromyalgia and arthritis</li>
            <li>Improved range of motion and flexibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vat__visual">
        <!-- Video placeholder -->
        <div class="vat__video-placeholder glass">
          <div class="vat__play-icon">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="23" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              <polygon points="20,16 34,24 20,32" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="vat__video-label">VAT Explainer Video</p>
          <p class="vat__video-sub">Coming soon</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vat__callout glass">
          <p class="vat__callout-text">
            <strong>Safe for most people.</strong> VAT is non-invasive, drug-free, and has
            no known side effects. It can be used alongside other treatments and therapies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .vat__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .vat__text {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .vat__how {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .vat__how-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vat__steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vat__step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .vat__step-num {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-teal);
    background: rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.08);
    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .vat__step h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .vat__step p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .vat__benefits h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .vat__benefit-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .vat__benefit-list li {
    padding: 0.625rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .vat__benefit-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-teal-light), var(--color-teal));
  }

  .vat__visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .vat__video-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.6), rgba(255,255,255,0.3));
  }

  .vat__play-icon {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .vat__video-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .vat__video-sub {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  .vat__callout {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vat__callout-text {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .vat__callout-text strong {
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .vat__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .vat__visual {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
